problem_text_cn: 如图,点A、B、C、D在圆O上,点E在AD的延长线上,若∠ABC=60°,则∠CDE的度数为()
problem_text_en: As shown in the figure, points A, B, C, and D are on circle O, and point E is on the extended line of AD. If ∠ABC = N_0, then the degree of ∠CDE is ()
raw_answer:
解:∵四边形ABCD为圆O的内接四边形,∴∠ABC+∠ADC=180°,∵∠CDE+∠ADC=180°,∠B=60°,∴∠CDE=∠B=60°,
